data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom/2 bathroom house is perfect for entertaining or family life. As you enter there is a foyer with storage and you see the open plan of the home clear to the back yard. Plenty of natural light. Visible is a fully equipped Kitchen with stone counters, newer stainless steel appliances, dark wood cabinets & a practical closet pantry offers lots of storage. Kitchen island overlooks to dinning and spacious living area that backs up to a beautiful yard. The sliding doors open to a small covered porch, perfect for outside grilling and a calm, private open area that does not back up to back door neighbors. The primary bedroom entrance is a bit separate from the other 2  bedrooms and the ample 4 piece bathroom they share. The primary bathroom has shower with shower doors. Separate laundry room offers space convenience. 2 car garage and parking driveway for 4 cars. All appliances are included. Residents have exclusive access to the HOA Community Pool, a perfect location to enjoy during the warm Florida summers or simply lounge poolside during the rest of the year! Central and close to shopping centers. House sits high with a no flood zone code. Location is key, as Fernanda Place is conveniently near I-4 and SR 415, providing easy access to Orlando's world-renowned theme parks and restaurant destinations. Additionally, the nearby Daytona Beach and New Smyrna Beach offer recreational opportunities! Come and see the conveniences this home offers!  Fernanda Drive can be your new home!
